data.description: Welcome to this exquisite 4-bedroom, 2-bath residence, tucked away at the end of a serene cul-de-sac. The home's exterior is a modern delight, featuring durable vinyl siding and an artfully landscaped yard embellished with smooth river rock. Stepping inside, the refinished hardwood floors glisten beneath your feet, reflecting the ambient glow of new fixtures above. Adding a rustic touch to the elegant setting is a newly installed barn door, a testament to the fine balance of modernity and timeless charm. The heart of this home - the kitchen - is a culinary artist's dream. Practically brand-new stainless steel appliances shine against the warm hue of butcherblock countertops. The open layout makes it an ideal space for family gatherings, encompassing both the kitchen and dining room in one setting. And for those beautiful mornings or laid-back evenings, the walk-out access to the covered patio provides an extended area for dining or relaxation. On the main level, three generously sized bedrooms await, including an oversized primary suite. This suite is the epitome of luxury, boasting its own private ensuite bathroom featuring a meticulously tiled shower. The expansive walk-in closet ensures ample storage, and the attached laundry room adds a touch of convenience to your daily routine. Journey downstairs and let your imagination run wild in the finished basement - perfect as a games room, home cinema, or simply a tranquil space to unwind. A versatile flex space offers endless possibilities, whether you envision a 4th bedroom, a home office, or a creative studio. Practicality meets functionality with the one-car drive-under garage and abundant storage options. This home is more than just a dwelling; it's a haven where memories will be made, laughter will be shared, and dreams will be realized. Don't miss the opportunity to make this dream your reality. Buyer/Buyers agent to verify all information.
